query:
INSERT INTO kanban_columns (id, project_id, board_id, name, slug, position, color, is_initial, is_terminal)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9)
               RETURNING id as "id!: Uuid",
                         project_id as "project_id!: Uuid",
                         board_id as "board_id: Uuid",
                         name,
                         slug,
                         position as "position!: i32",
                         color,
                         is_initial as "is_initial!: bool",
                         is_terminal as "is_terminal!: bool",
                         created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                         updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
